b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":2443,"category_name":"News","pr_category_id":"1","title_name":"3rd Anniversary Events Are Coming! [Addendum] ","message":"<div><span style=\\"color: rgb(41, 105, 176);\\"><strong>[Addendum <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1635929400\\"><\/span>]<\/strong><\/span><br>We have corrected the following issue in the summon information of the Dragalia Scratch-A-Thon summon.<br><br>[Before correction]<br>Once obtained from the Dragalia Scratch-A-Thon, a Scratch-A-Thon summon can be used to summon one 5\\u2605 unit.<br><br>[After correction]<br>Once obtained from the Dragalia Scratch-A-Thon, a Scratch-A-Thon summon can be used to summon one 5\\u2605 dragon.<br><br>Thank you for your understanding.<\/div><hr><div>The following events for the 3rd anniversary will start on <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1632722400\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/43a441027bc4ebbf12f48b184eb3c906.png\\"><\/div><div><br><\/div><hr><div>1. Announcing a Platinum Showcase! 5\\u2605 Gala Dragalia Adventurer Guaranteed!<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>A Platinum Showcase is on the way! A 5\\u2605 Gala Dragalia adventurer available when this summon showcase begins is guaranteed to appear in the tenfold summon.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>The roster for this summon showcase does not include the new adventurer or dragon from the Gala Dragalia showcase starting on <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1632981600\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Event Duration<\/div><div><span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1632722400\\"><\/span> to <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1634536799\\"><\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><hr><div>2. Announcing Gala Dragalia!<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>The initial appearance rate for 5\\u2605 adventurers and dragons will be boosted to 6%, which is up from the standard 4%!<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Event Duration<\/div><div><span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1632722400\\"><\/span> to <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1632981599\\"><\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>The adventurer Gala Zethia and the dragon Gala Bahamut will be featured in the Gala Dragalia starting on <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1632981600\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Event Duration<\/div><div><span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1632981600\\"><\/span> to <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1633413599\\"><\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>In the Gala Dragalia starting on <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1632722400\\"><\/span>, players may exchange wyrmsigils for Gala Dragalia adventurers or certain Gala Dragalia dragons who were available when the event began.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Wyrmsigils may only be redeemed in the summon showcase from which they were earned. Wyrmsigils earned from the Gala Dragalia starting on <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1632722400\\"><\/span> cannot be redeemed in the Gala Dragalia starting on <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1632981600\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><hr><div>3. Presenting 3rd Anniversary Packs!<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Anniversary packs will be available for a limited time under Value Packs in the Shop starting on <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1632722400\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Availability Period<\/div><div><span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1632722400\\"><\/span> to <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1635487199\\"><\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><hr><div>4. A Daily Free Tenfold Summon and Free Hundredfold Summon Are Coming!<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>A daily free tenfold summon event, which allows you to perform a tenfold summon on the applicable summon showcase for free once per day, starts on <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1632722400\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>What&#39;s more, there will be a free hundredfold summon event, during which you can perform one hundred summons on the applicable summon showcase for free, on <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1636005600\\"><\/span>.<span style=\\"color: rgb(226, 80, 65);\\">&nbsp;Note that this event only lasts for a single day, so don&#39;t miss it!<\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Event Duration<\/div><div>\\u30fbDaily Free Tenfold Summon<\/div><div><span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1632722400\\"><\/span> to <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1636005599\\"><\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbFree Hundredfold Summon<\/div><div><span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1636005600\\"><\/span> to <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1636091999\\"><\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><hr><div>5. The 3rd Anniversary Bonus is Coming!<br><br>You can get the following rewards when you log in during the event duration.<br><br>\\u25a0Daily Rewards<br>Day 1: 5\\u2605 Wyrmprint: Third Anniversary! &times; 1<br>Day 2: Wyrmite &times; 1,500<br>Day 3: Mini Jupi &times; 1<br>Day 4: Rupie &times; 30,000,000<br>Day 5: Omnicite &times; 1<br>Day 6: Blessed Ethon Ashes &times; 30<br>Day 7: Talonstone &times; 300<br>Day 8: Champion&#39;s Testament &times; 3<br>Day 9: Eldwater &times; 100,000<br>Day 10: Damascus Ingot &times; 1<br><br>\\u25a0Event Duration<br><span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1632722400\\"><\/span> to <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1634104799\\"><\/span><br><br>In addition, the dragon Mini Mercs will be added to the fafnir medals section of the Treasure Trade.<br><br>Notes:<br>1. The log-in bonus will be sent to you every day after 07:00 when you log in.<br>2. Gifts sent as log-in bonuses can only be accepted for a limited time.<br>3. The 5\\u2605 wyrmprint &quot;Third Anniversary!&quot; will be gifted directly to you instead of being sent to your goodie box.<br><br><\/div><hr><div>6. A Dragalia Scratch-A-Thon is Coming!<br><br>A Dragalia Scratch-A-Thon starts on <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1632722400\\"><\/span>. During this event, log in for a chance to win items and wyrmite. If you manage to win a Scratch-A-Thon Summon, head on over to the summon screen to summon a 5\\u2605dragon. Don&#39;t fret if luck isn&#39;t on your side, though&mdash;if you haven&#39;t won a Scratch-A-Thon Summon by the time the final day rolls around, you&#39;ll get one guaranteed!<br><br>\\u25a0Prize Lineup<br>\\u30fbScratch-A-Thon Summon<br>\\u30fbRupie &times; 1,000,000<br>\\u30fbExquisite Honey &times; 5<br>\\u30fbWyrmite &times; 50<br>\\u30fbRainbow Orb &times; 25<br>\\u30fbEldwater &times; 1,000<br>\\u30fbChampion&#39;s Testament &times; 1<br><br>\\u25a0Event Duration<br>\\u30fbDragalia Scratch-A-Thon<br><span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1632722400\\"><\/span> to <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1636005599\\"><\/span><br><br>\\u30fbScratch-A-Thon Summon<br><span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1632722400\\"><\/span> to <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1636955999\\"><\/span><br><br>\\u25a0Notes<br>1. The Dragalia Scratch-A-Thon prize will be available every day after 07:00 when you log in.<br>2. Dragalia Scratch-A-Thon prizes can only be accepted for a limited time.<br>3. Each Scratch-A-Thon Summon session can only be performed once. Multiple sessions will stack for the duration of the event.<br><br><\/div><hr><div>7. The Faith Forsaken (Part One) Raid Event Is Coming!<br><br>Don&#39;t miss this limited-time raid event. Take on event-specific quests to defeat the light-attuned raid boss and earn rewards!<br><br>\\u25a0Event Duration<br><span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1632981600\\"><\/span> to <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1634104799\\"><\/span><br><br><\/div><hr><div>8. 3rd Anniversary Stickers Are Coming!<br><br>Stickers themed after the 3rd anniversary will be added on <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1632722400\\"><\/span>.<br><br>To see the new stickers, select Player Info under Menu at the top of the screen in-game, then select Stickers and see the Available Stickers section. To use the new stickers, edit your Sticker Loadout, which is also under Stickers.<br><br><\/div><hr><div>9. Resetting the Social Reward in Co-op!<br><br>We will reset the number of times players can obtain the social reward, which can be obtained by playing co-op with another player for the first time, on <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1632722400\\"><\/span>.<br><br>After clearing a quest, you can get 50 wyrmite per player (up to 50 times). You can get a total of 2,500, so be sure to play co-op!<br><br><\/div><hr><div>10. Presenting 3rd Anniversary Upgrade Events!<br><br>Starting on <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1632722400\\"><\/span>, a triple-drops event for Avenue to Power and a triple-rupies event for Avenue to Fortune will be held alongside many other events, such as triple-drops and half-stamina events for certain main campaign chapters.<\/div><div><br><\/div><hr><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1632454200,"prev_article_id":"2462","next_article_id":"2498","image_path":"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/43a441027bc4ebbf12f48b184eb3c906.png","update_time":1636335705}}}'